This directory contains the source files for chapter 5. This includes 

thrd.c

which is the Pthread program shown in Figure  5.7. to run this program, enter

gcc thrd.c -lpthread
./a.out <int>

i.e.

./a.out 5

The Java programs correspond to programs shown in this Chapter.

The ipc directory contains the complete multithreaded solution to the BoundedBuffer problem using message
passing. To run this example, first compile all source files and then enter

	java Factory 
